data.description: This one-story home situated on a spacious corner lot is waiting for you to start enjoying life by the lake! The open concept living, kitchen and dining area with large windows is great for entertaining or hosting family gatherings. If you enjoy being outdoors, the expansive deck is the perfect place to relax or enjoy your morning coffee and provides a small lake view. The home has a functional floor plan with three bedrooms and two full bathrooms providing room for guests or to convert a room into a home office/study. The two-car attached garage has room for vehicles, your golf cart or the lake toys. Located in the gated community of Cape Royale, you can enjoy use of the deep water marina, parks, tennis courts, swimming pool, basketball court, nature tail and more!
